	</text>
	<text id="nav_text" x="218" y="425" width="562" height="" autosize="H" style="PROMPT" visible="false" fx="PROMPT_SHOW" hidefx="PROMPT_HIDE">
		<content translate="true">&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;Click a &lt;B&gt;Lesson&lt;/B&gt; or &lt;B&gt;Activity&lt;/B&gt; to learn more about &lt;B&gt;The Five Steps of Emotion Coaching&lt;/B&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
	</text>
	<section id="presentation_text" align="" spacing="0" autospace="false" columns="0" exclusive="false" expanded="true">
		<text id="text01" x="25" y="50" width="388" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Parents can use emotional moments as opportunities to connect with their child. Many parents can share a child's happiness when they have learned a new skill.</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text02" x="25" y="110.8" width="365" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">These emotional moments are when children need to turn to adults and caregivers for guidance.</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text03" x="25" y="156" width="362" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Suggestions for connecting:&lt;LI&gt;Talk to your child at eye level.&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text04" x="25" y="186" width="387" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">&lt;LI&gt;Explain your mistakes, repair the interaction, and reconnect with the child.&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text05" x="25" y="230" width="387" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Children's emotions offer parents important opportunities to: &lt;LI&gt;Understand the child &lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Build a deeper and more trusting relationship &lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Teach children about feelings &lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
	</section>
